<!--Display a container with a _header and dog grooming information-->
<div class="main-container">
    <h1>Dog Boarding Services:</h1>
    <div class="service-summary">
        <p class="summary">Our boarding services provide a safe and loving environment for your dog throughout their stay.
            We offer both doggy daycare and short or long-term boarding, during which, dogs are given monitored socialization
            time where they get to play with their fellow boarders. Our facility features a 24/7 video monitoring system that owners will
            be given access to upon dropping their dog(s) off, all to ensure that every dog is cared for to the best of our abilities. 
           <br>
           <br>
           Dogs boarded with us are fed the same high-quality foods that are sold at Pets-R-Us, and our socialization area is filled with
           a wide variety of toys to help keep our boarders happy and content during their stay. 
           We also offer daily photo update texts for each dog boarded with us along with written status reports available upon request, 
           so owners can rest at ease knowing that their dog is receiving only the best care while they're away, because at Pets-R-Us, 
           your dog's well-being is our highest concern.
           <br>
           <br>
           Our pricing tiers cover boarding for one, two, or three dogs. For questions about other arrangements, please call us at 111-222-333.
        </p>
        <!--Display and center a photo of our hypothetical dog trainer-->
        <div class="center-image">
            <img src="../public/images/boarding.jpg" alt="Photo of dog in a dog crate" height="350" width="450">
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

